== Urutare Rwa Ngarama ==
[[Urutare rwa Ngarama|Urutare]] rwa Ngarama ruherereye muntara yi Burasirazuba mukarere ka [[Gatsibo (Akarere)|Gatsibo]] mumurenge wa Ngarama 

mukagari ka Ngarama mu mudugudu wa Ibare<ref>https://www.rwandagorillasafaris.com/blog/urutare-rwa-ngarama.html</ref> uru Rutare ruzwi cyane mu mateka yu Rwanda

== Amateka ==
[[Urutare rwa Ngarama]] ni urutare ruvugwaho amateka menshi atandukanye cyane ko bavugako ariho

Ngarama wari umugaragu wu Mwami [[Ruganzu II Ndoli|Ruganzu]] ariho yiciye Saruhara rwa Nkomokomo<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/182947</ref>

== Aho ruherereye ==
Urutare rwa Ngarama ruherereye m' [[Umurenge wa Kimisagara|umurenge]] wa Ngarama mu Kagari ka Ibare uvuye mubyapa bya Ngarama <ref>http://thebridge.rw/urutare-ngarama-yivuganiyeho-saruhara-rwa-nkomokomo/</ref>

ni hagati ya  kirometero 20

== Ubukerarugendo ==
Urutare rwa Ngarama ni urutare rusurwa cyane kuko rukoreshwa no muburezi kuko rwigirwaho nabana bakiri bato

